Census block group shapefiles

sf-blockgroup.Rd

TIGER/Line shapefiles for census block groups in Kansas City, Missouri, downloaded from census.gov and modified using get_kc_sf().

The US Census Bureau uses the Global Coordinate System North American Datum of 1983 (GCS NAD83/EPSG: 4269).

Usage

sf_blockgroup_2018

sf_blockgroup_2019

sf_blockgroup_2020

sf_blockgroup_2021

sf_blockgroup_2022

sf_blockgroup_2023

sf_blockgroup_2024
